Damn Monkey is a game inspired by the famous arcade game, Donkey Kong.



/****************************************************************************
* BUILDING DAMN MONKEY                                                      *
****************************************************************************/

BUILD DEPENDENCIES:

    To be built, Damn Monkey needs the following dependencies:
        * SDL <http://www.libsdl.org/>,
        * SDL Image <http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/>
        * SDL Mixer <http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_mixer>


BUILD ON LINUX:

    Just type the `make` command from in the Damn Monkey directory.


